name: Reservation Dogs
overview: Four Indigenous teenagers in rural Oklahoma steal, rob and save in order to get to the exotic, mysterious and faraway land of California.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: In season three, the Rez Dogs find themselves stranded in Cali and have to figure out their way back home. After making it back to Okern, Elora considers the idea of college, Bear comes across a conspiracy theorist named Maximus, Willie Jack grows more invested in healing her community, and Cheese, well, he still lives with his grandmother whoâ€™s not his grandmother. Meanwhile, the aunties, uncles and elders explore their pasts and try to heal old wounds.
